    "long_instructions": "## AI as a Hiring Manager\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to choose which two candidates to interview. \r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Add the PDF with the six resumes into AI Chat. Come up with a prompt to have AI read through the resumes and select two applicants to interview. \r\n2. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's response.\r\n3. Find the section in your Activity Guide called \"AI’s Selections\" and answer the questions.\r\n4. Revise your prompt to AI Chat and have it prioritize the same things you did. \r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n",
